            "text": "<p>This interest in beauty has motivated illycaffè’s contribution to promoting art and culture by supporting artists, institutions and international exhibits. Seeking out new beauty, finding it, sharing it and celebrating it: these are the goals that set our entrepreneurial culture apart. We have been partners of the Venice Biennale since 2003, one of the world’s most important and prestigious international exhibitions of contemporary art, organised every two years by the Biennale Foundation. </p><p>We also support leading international contemporary art fairs, like Turin’s Artissima, ArcoMadrid, Asia Now, Paris International and Frieze, which has exhibited in London, New York, Los Angeles and Seoul</p>",
